string 12648 ^8Jane: ^0It's not as good as my yaught but...it will do.
string 12649 ^8Jane: ^0Let's get hovering.

string 12650 ^8Jane: ^0Ice of you to drop by.
string 12651 ^8Jane: ^0Ooh...frosty.
string 12652 ^8Jane: ^0You're burning up!
string 12653 ^8Jane: ^0OOh, spicy!
string 12654 ^8Jane: ^0Feel the burn!
string 12655 ^8Jane: ^0Fire is indeed hot.
string 12656 ^8Jane: ^0It's coming for you.
string 12657 ^8Jane: ^0I see you!
string 12658 ^8Jane: ^0Now where do you think you're going?
string 12659 ^8Jane: ^0Ooh..I wonder what this does?

string 12660 ^8Jane: ^0What a thrill.
string 12661 ^8Jane: ^0What a thrill...
string 12662 ^8Jane: ^0I'm bad to the bone, baby.
string 12663 ^8Jane: ^0Oh shit!
string 12664 ^8Jane: ^0Oh shit.
string 12665 ^8Jane: ^0Fuck! God damn ghosts!
string 12666 ^8Jane: ^0Aagh!
string 12667 ^8Jane: ^0You git! God damn ghosts.
string 12668 ^8Jane: ^0Time for a close encounter.
string 12669 ^8Jane: ^0Terminated, motherfucker!

string 12670 ^8Jane: ^0Terminated!
string 12671 ^8Jane: ^0Ooh, sparks.
string 12672 ^8Jane: ^0What an electrifying way to go.
string 12673 ^8Jane: ^0What shocking behaviour.
string 12674 ^8Jane: ^0Electrifying!
string 12675 ^8Jane: ^0...Running low on air.
string 12676 ^8Jane: ^0...Gonna need a new tank of air.
string 12677 ^8Jane: ^0Shit, I'm almost out of oxygen.
string 12678 ^8Jane: ^0Great, an O2 canister!
string 12679 ^8Jane: ^0Damnit, I tripped the alarm!

string 12680 ^8Jane: ^0Now that was a rookie mistake.
string 12681 ^8Jane: ^0A few pounds in my pocket wouldn't go amiss.
string 12682 ^8Jane: ^0In for a penny, in for a pound.
string 12683 ^8Jane: ^0I better take this to the lab.
string 12684 ^8Jane: ^0I bet the lab boys would like this.
string 12685 ^8Jane: ^0Just my luck, the battery's nearly dead.
string 12686 ^8Jane: ^0Bet I could boot this boulder and get it moving...
string 12687 ^8Jane: ^0Bugger, the gun's overheating!
string 12688 ^8Jane: ^0OOh that's hot, oww!
string 12689 ^8Jane: ^0Ugh, I hate getting soaked.

string 12690 ^8Jane: ^0Of course it's raining...
string 12691 ^8Jane: ^0Maybe I should raid some tombs with these.
string 12692 ^8Jane: ^0Let's set you down...here.
string 12693 ^8Jane: ^0*tut* oh and I just polished these!
string 12694 ^8Jane: ^0Well that wasn't annoying at all!
string 12695 ^8Jane: ^0Ah huh!
string 12696 ^8Jane: ^0I hope it's something good.
string 12697 ^8Jane: ^0Damn it I've been cursed!
string 12698 ^8Jane: ^0How dare you curse me!
string 12699 ^8Jane: ^0Open sesame!

string 12700 ^8Jane: ^0Knock knock, hope you don't mind.
string 12701 ^8Jane: ^0Alright, let's go!
string 12702 ^8Jane: ^0Hope you like surprises cuz' this one's going to blow you away.
string 12703 ^8Jane: ^0It's judgement day!
string 12704 ^8Jane: ^0Let's go!
string 12705 ^8Jane: ^0Giddy up!
string 12706 ^8Jane: ^0Woah, woah!
string 12707 ^8Jane: ^0Care to test your mettle?
string 12708 ^8Jane: ^0Taste my steel!
string 12709 ^8Jane: ^0Come on then!

string 12710 ^8Jane: ^0Arms up and Queensbury rules, let's go!
string 12711 ^8Jane: ^0Ah that was close...
string 12712 ^8Jane: ^0Oh fuck it!
string 12713 ^8Jane: ^0Bollocks!
string 12714 ^8Jane: ^0Hell yeah, that's what it's all about!
string 12715 ^8Jane: ^0Shield is down...not good.
string 12716 ^8Jane: ^0Now I regret not joining the Wing divers unit.
string 12717 ^8Jane: ^0I can't see!
string 12718 ^8Jane: ^0Damnit I'm blinded!
string 12719 ^8Jane: ^0Damn, my electronics are down!

string 12720 ^8Jane: ^0Oh great, an EMP, just what I need.
string 12721 ^8Jane: ^0Hmph, very cute.
string 12722 ^8Jane: ^0Those are *adorable*.
string 12723 ^8Jane: ^0Wanker!
